Daemos stood before Belthassan, Melchana and Tankor. His new 
self-appointed command did not please them, but they would have to 
deal with it.

Daemos: You know that the original harvesting mission still stands. 
Upon my arrival, I have planted energon seeds. The fruits should be 
ripe by now. I need someone to go gather them. The urgency of the 
moment, with the Infecticon demonstration of power, has really shown 
us that we need to gather as much energon as we can in what little 
time we have.

Melchana: I could take the Hellgate and bring the fruits back. That 
is, IF you do not appose your veto, O, revered Commander.

Belthassan: Shut up, sister. Yes, this was not a group decision, but 
it was what the Matrix decided...

Tankor: Matrix, Shmatrix...

Belthassan glared at Tankor, venom in his eyes.

Daemos: Melchana, gather the fruits. Belthassan, you are my second 
officer. Come with me and I will ezplain why I do all this. Tankor, 
contact Zardus to know what he wishes to do about the Infecticons.

Little did he know that Zardus has been missing for some times 
already.

Thus, the Hellgate departed for France.

Tankor: This is a message to Zardus. The Tripredacus wish to know what 
your actions will be towards the Infecticons.
